Clarity: this is basically how stuff like negative space, color, fonts and graphics help bring focus on the main content without making the screen too cluttered.\
Deference: this is ability to interact with the content without much difficulty.\
Depth: this is the ability to have content layered over each other and the user being able to easily guide through the transitions.\
